main event: An unidentified flying object was observed moving at high speeds and disappearing instantaneously in Onawa, Iowa.
interesting points: The object was described as a curved half oval, appearing as large as a commercial jet,It was white in color with a small white light in the rear,The object was first sighted in the east and vanished into the east,It exhibited erratic zigzag movements,The object appeared dazzlingly bright and had a fuzzy outline.
sighted object: curved half oval object with a small white light
witness description: The observer reported the sighting but did not provide a name in the document.
